{{Other uses|Billiatt (disambiguation){{!}}Billiatt}} __NOTOC__ {{Use Australian English|date=January 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date= January 2015}} {{Infobox Australian place | type = protected | name = Billiatt Wilderness Protection Area | state = sa | iucn_category = Ib | image = | caption = | image_alt = | coordinates = {{coord|35.013867266|S|140.390333169|E|format=dms|display=inline,title}}<ref name=CAPAD2016SASum>{{cite web|title= Terrestrial Protected Areas of South Australia (refer 'DETAIL' tab ) |url= http://www.environment.gov.au/system/files/pages/761994ab-42cc-4f24-952c-c21221861884/files/capad2016sa.xlsx |work=CAPAD 2016|publisher=Australian Government, Department of the Environment (DoE) |accessdate=21 February 2018 |date=2016}}</ref> | force_national_map = | relief = | pushpin_map_caption = | pushpin_label_position = | map_alt = | nearest_town_or_city = [[Alawoona, South Australia|Alawoona]]<ref name=LMV>{{cite web|title= Search results for 'Billiatt Wilderness Protection Area' with the following datasets selected – ‘Suburbs and Localities’, ‘NPW and Conservation Properties‘ and 'Gazetteer’ |url= http://location.sa.gov.au/viewer/?map=roads&x=140.90912&y=-35.04814&z=10&uids=41,19,105&pinx=140.471010&piny=-34.964910&pinTitle=Location&pinText=Billiatt+Wilderness+Protection+Area,+Park |website=Location SA Map Viewer |publisher=Government of South Australian Government |accessdate=11 May 2018}}</ref> | area = 591.25 | area_footnotes = <ref name=ReserveList>{{cite web|title=Protected Areas Information System - reserve list (as of 17 Feb 2014)|url=http://www.environment.sa.gov.au/files/b88e6e26-4bd9-4c68-8fff-9e800114eb69/park-management-protected-areas-gen.pdf|publisher=Department of Environment Water and Natural Resources|accessdate=26 March 2014|pages=}}</ref> | established = {{start date|2008|7|24|df=y}} | established_footnotes = <ref name=2012-13report/><ref name="SAGG-2008">{{cite web|title=Wilderness Protection (Billiatt Wilderness Protection Area) Proclamation 2008|url=http://classic.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/sa/proc/wpwpap2008709/|website=The South Australian Government Gazette|publisher=South Australian Government|accessdate=10 May 2018|page=3476|date=24 July 2008}}</ref> | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | visitation_footnotes = | managing_authorities = [[Department of Environment and Water (South Australia)|Department of Environment and Water]] | url = | footnotes = }} '''Billiatt Wilderness Protection Area''' is a [[protected area]] located about {{convert|30|km|abbr=off}} north of [[Lameroo, South Australia|Lameroo]] in [[South Australia]].<ref name=gazateer>{{Gazetteer of Australia|name= Billiatt Wilderness Protection Area |feature= SA0083132 }}</ref><ref name=2012-13report>{{cite journal|title=Wilderness Advisory Committee Annual Report 2012-13|date=September 2013|page =14|url=http://www.environment.sa.gov.au/files/5ad5624b-73b3-4284-86e0-a28900c9111c/wilderness-annual-report-2012-13-rep.pdf|accessdate=17 March 2014|issn=1832-9357}}</ref>
The wilderness protection area occupies in land in the gazetted localities of [[Billiatt, South Australia|Billiatt]], [[Lameroo, South Australia|Lameroo]] and [[Sandalwood, South Australia|Sandalwood]].<ref name=LMV/>
The wilderness protection area was proclaimed under the ''Wilderness Protection Act 1992'' on 24 July 2008 on land excised from the [[Billiatt Conservation Park]].<ref name=MP>{{cite web|title=Reserves of the Billiatt District Management Plan 2011|url=http://www.environment.sa.gov.au/files/435d3047-1216-475c-9aca-9f8f00d964a5/cons-gen-billiatmgmtplan.pdf|publisher=Department of Environment and Natural Resources|accessdate=11 January 2015|page=1}}</ref>
It is classified as an [[International Union for Conservation of Nature|IUCN]] [[IUCN protected area categories#Category Ib — Wilderness Area|Category Ib protected area]].<ref name=CAPAD2016SASum/>
