'''''Gobius hypselosoma''''' is a species of [[goby]] native to fresh and brackish waters of [[Madagascar]] and the [[Mascarene Islands]]. It can reach a length of {{convert|25|cm|in}} [[fish measurement|TL]].<ref>{{FishBase |genus= Gobius|species= hypselosoma| month = June | year = 2013}}</ref>
