'''Håvard Kjærstad''' (born 1947) is a [[Norwegia]]n businessperson.
He graduated from [[BI Norwegian Business School]] in 1972 with a degree in [[business economy]]. He was employed at [[Esso]] in 1970 and is currently Nordic Retail Sales Manager. He is also chairman of the board at the [[Norwegian Petroleum Institute]].<ref>[http://www.np.no/ktml2/files/uploads/Diverse/NPs%20styre%20hjemmeside.pdf The board of the Norwegian Petroleum Institute]{{dead link|date=November 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
Kjærstad has a fortune of [[$]]1.22 million.<ref>[http://tjenester.aftenposten.no/skatteliste/search.htm?id=23465203&method=findPerson Tax lists of Norway, 2006]</ref>
